        mkpreview
        ==================
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/github/v/release/:cbitterfield/:mkpreview?sort=semver
                :target: https://pypi.org/project/mkpreview/
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/fgriberi/python_boilerplate.svg
